      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the absolute joy of driving her. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014I\u2019ve babied her from day one, always kept her tucked away in the garage and polished to a mirror finish. She runs like a dream and looks even better in person. There might be a tiny, tiny speck here or there if you look with a magnifying glass, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as you\u2019ll ever find. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate her as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
