    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide through winding coastal roads, the engine humming a low, rhythmic lullaby that speaks of a golden era. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule, a masterpiece of chrome and leather that captures the very essence of freedom. Every curve of its polished body reflects a history of elegance, while the interior welcomes you with the scent of fine materials and the promise of adventure. To drive it is to command the road, a symphony of engineering and artistry that feels as though it were birthed just yesterday. It is more than a vehicle\u2014it is a legacy waiting to be written.",
      "price": 48500.0,
