    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Thanks for stopping by. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new owner to enjoy the magic. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept and pampered like a member of the family. It\u2019s in truly stunning shape, looking and driving just like it did when it first left the showroom. You might find a tiny, microscopic mark if you really hunt for it, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in top-tier condition, you\u2019ve found your match. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 48500.0,
