    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3, a pinnacle of the S54 inline-six legacy. This chassis has been fastidiously maintained with a zero-tolerance approach to wear. The high-revving 3.2L powerplant exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, delivering that signature metallic rasp through a pristine exhaust path. We've proactively addressed the common weak points: the Vanos system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been fully reinforced to handle the torsional loads. The Getrag 6-speed shifts with surgical precision, paired with a limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. The suspension geometry is dialed, featuring refreshed bushings that ensure the communicative steering feel these cars are legendary for. This isn't just a driver; it\u2019s a blue-chip investment for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
